---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';
import MarkdownContent from '../../../components/MarkdownContent.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Part-Time Equipment Business 2026',
  slug: 'part-time-equipment-business-2026',
  excerpt: 'Part-time equipment business financing 2026. Side business equipment loans for part-time operators.',
  date: '2026-01-07',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 3,
  category: 'Equipment Financing',
  image: '/images/blog/part-time.jpg'
};

const keywords = ["machinery-financing","part-time","side-business"],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];

const markdownContent = `
# Part-Time Equipment Business 2026

Part-time equipment business? Financing available for side-business operators in 2026.

## Part-Time Equipment Reality

**Common Situations:**
- Main job + part-time contracting
- Weekend equipment rental
- Seasonal equipment use
- Building business part-time

## 2026 Part-Time Solutions

**Approval Based On:**
- Combined income (job + business)
- Equipment rental income potential
- Business viability
- **40-50% approval rate**

## Real Part-Time Approvals

**Case:** Full-time driver + weekend excavator rental
**Income:** RM 5k (job) + RM 3k (rental)
**Equipment:** Komatsu PC200 (rental business)
**Financing:** RM 180,000, 20% down, 6 years

## Part-Time Interest

| Income Stability | Rate | Down Payment |
|----------------|------|--------------|
| **Stable dual income** | 5.5-6.5% | 10-20% |
| **Seasonal** | 6.5-7.5% | 20-30% |
| **Variable** | 7.5-8.5% | 30-50% |

## Get Part-Time Equipment

Part-time equipment business? Apply for combined income equipment financing.

---

**Full-time business?** See [1-Year Business Equipment](/blog/1-year-business-equipment-2026).
`;
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Equipment Financing</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <MarkdownContent content={markdownContent} />

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton href="/en/contact">Apply for Equipment Financing</CTAButton>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
